race.comment: LAKEVIEW LEIGH (1) turned in a moderate run last time when sixth at this track over 435m behind Scampi (25.48). Rates on top in this line up. MINTER'S JET (8) turned in a better run last time to find a minor placing (26.33) at Warragul behind Rapid Invader in a Maiden. Has the early speed to give a sight. The form from his last run is stacking up nicely. Expected to feature. MR. TEDDY BEAR (6) stalked the lead from the inside draw before finishing second last start (26.22) at Warragul in Maiden over 460m. Leading chance. ERRATIC KAREN (7) is a Leanne Burke-trained newcomer by Whiskey Riot out of Americano Miss. Start all important and will need some luck getting across from the wide draw. Profiles well so pay to keep very safe.
